During and following [[Age of Enlightenment]] people largely forgotten the relationship 宗教与教育。[[让-雅克·卢梭]] fuelled an influential early-[[Romanticism]] reaction to formalised religion-based education at a time when the concept of [[childhood]] had started to become popular as a distinct aspect of [[child development|human development]].

[[波兰-立陶宛 Commonwealth]]的[[Commission of 国民教育]] (波兰语: ''Komisja Edukacji Narodowej''，立陶宛语：''Nacionaline Edukacine Komisija'') formed in [[1773年]] counts as 人类历史上第一个[[教育部]]。-->
